      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically robust, featuring a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including Vanos system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains composed thanks to upgraded bushings and a tuned suspension geometry, ensuring precise turn-in and feedback. While the exterior reflects its age with minor cosmetic patina, the powertrain delivers linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience. A purist\u2019s specification for those who prioritize mechanical integrity and driving dynamics.",
